{"tid":110583,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"何謂朋友","createTime":"2017-02-06T19:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T15:43:49.000Z","uid":36374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef175b373c1e9be4401189da876dc12381b27aa","tid":110583,"uid":36374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T19:27:06.000Z","msg":"以前中學一班打機朋友，<br />\n每日放學番去就組隊打信長，<br />\n打war3 , 後來就打lol.<br />\n第日番學就討論劇情。<br />\n以為可以做到一生一世既朋友，<br />\n中學畢業，大家開始厭倦打機，<br />\n愈黎愈少見，疏遠晒。<br />\n或者係，係新環境搵到另一班朋友。<br />\n正如最佳損友一口歌詞，<br />\n位置變了，各有隊友。<br />\n好似除左打機已經再冇其他話題，<br />\n好似酒肉朋友一樣，<br />\n冇酒肉冇朋友，<br />\n只係酒肉變左打機。"},{"pid":"ca1b1233b86ffc64759d8cdbad7de57f1415fc9a","tid":110583,"uid":74455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T19:30:49.000Z","msg":"每個人都只會係你生命中既過客<br />\n冇人可以永遠陪住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee7c6e875e8dc490bb3baad4154df3d7f6a7f15","tid":110583,"uid":77942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T19:34:25.000Z","msg":"所以先要珍惜現在"},{"pid":"7cd17a856e2a36b38b149781f23771ed8752810d","tid":110583,"uid":74455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T19:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以先要珍惜現在</blockquote><br />\n活在當下係最重要 但係人偏偏鐘意諗多一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dffd31b4dbad950a0022bd5a82b071d559bf0c","tid":110583,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T19:45:19.000Z","msg":"總要有人努力維繫"},{"pid":"a11b40be0998de02034ac8429315ed49e79bfc02","tid":110583,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T19:47:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edd67b16fbf7407e0946bb688f0e8851b325633a","tid":110583,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T19:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>總要有人努力維繫</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac